sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor U as User
  participant UI as UI
  participant K as Kong
  participant A as Auth Service
  participant SQL as SQL DB

  U->>UI: Login
  UI->>K: POST /api/v1/auth/login
  K->>A: forward
  A->>SQL: verify user
  A-->>K: 200 JWT access token
  K-->>UI: JWT
  Note over UI: Bearer on next API calls
